This is a valid point. I have suggested that this be addressed, but the best you guys (the clerics) have come up with is no consecutive clerics from the same guild. Personally I don't think that is enough, and there should be a limit per guild. On thinking of it maybe something like one slot per guild + one slot per 5 epicless 51+ cleric they have guilded. Or something. But it's not my call.<br>
<br>
