<br>
There may be some truth to this. It's human nature to help your friends. But you can't change it from the outside. Join up and lobby for some tweaks.<br>
<br>
Jlail, the thing is, without the list GS will not be getting many epics. At least not for free. High AA toons and luclin gear means it is very easy for some guilds to get these mobs if they want. I doubt VM or LC would care, but there are others that would. And they don't need to send many people. I don't see how a guild like GS, who I have great respect for, will be able to compete in a FFA system.<br>
<br>
I think the cleric list needs to address the concerns you have, but I don't think doing away with it is a good idea.<br>
